chapter.para:
Grizzly's runtime dependences are categorized into the following:


Core framework. The Grizzly core module. The rest of Grizzly modules depend on
                    it;



HTTP framework. The HTTP Codec implementation;



HTTP Server framework. Grizzly HTTP server implementation;



HTTP Servlet framework. Basic Grizzly based Servlet support;



Port unification;



Comet;



WebSockets;
